  "instructions_to_main_agent": "You are building a high-performance fitness tool. It should feel like a cockpit or a HUD (Heads-Up Display). Avoid 'friendly' or 'cute' aesthetics. Go for 'Cyberpunk Sport'. Use the provided images for the landing page and dashboard placeholders. The 'Scan Food' feature is the core value prop - make it accessible instantly."
